Would you be satisfied with a tiny home or off grid cabin made from a shipping container?

This one is in Dallas and the interior is actually pretty elegantly designed with rustic varnished boards, modern kitchen appliances, and sleek white bath finishes. 
Theres a cozy master bedroom with a queen sized bed and a built in nightstand. Even has a small closet area to keep your clothes wrinkle free. 
A brilliantly designed second room doubles as a lofted bedroom and a living room.
